28 SECTION 2. EXTRA HELP - OPERATIONS. There is hereby authorized, for
29 the Department of Human Services - Division of County Operations - Operations
30 for the 2025-2026 fiscal year, the following maximum number of part-time or
31 temporary employees, to be known as "Extra Help", payable from funds
32 appropriated herein for such purposes: forty-three (43) temporary or part-
33 time employees, when needed, at rates of pay not to exceed those provided in
34 the Uniform Classification and Compensation Act, or its successor, or this
35 act for the appropriate classification.
